title: The Jam: Special (1987 One-shot) - Bernie Mireault
description:
This book consists of 32 pages of reprint material, four 'Jam' stories which saw print as back-up strips in 'New Triumph featuring Northguard' and a new thirteen page story.

'The Jam" went on to a regular series as "The Jam: Urban Adventures" which saw print via Slave Labor, Tundra, Dark Horse and Caliber Press all the while keeping the numerical sequence.

Enjoy
